♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,
I don't mind ♪

07:44.353 --> 07:48.055
♪ Me and Missy is
so busy, busy making money ♪

07:48.057 --> 07:49.523
♪ All right ♪

07:49.559 --> 07:55.396
♪ All step back,
I'm 'bout to dance ♪

07:55.398 --> 07:57.198
♪ The greenback boogie ♪

